CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 27, 1957, page A13, reads: "Iotas' Dinner - Members of Iota Phi Lambda Sorority gave a charming dinner at the Greene Hearthe, celebrating National Business Week of the group, and honoring Marion Jordon. Pictured are Mrs. Lois Lee Dorsey, Councilman Paul F. Jones, Mrs. Jordon, Charles A. Carpenter. the speaker; Phi Chapter president, Jeanne Farrish, and Anne Penn... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, including members of the lota Phi Lambda Sorority, left to right, Lois Lee Dorsey, Councilman Paul F. Jones, Marion Jordon, Charles A. Carpenter, Phi Chapter president Jeanne or Jean Farrish, and Anne Penn, gathered at the Greene Hearth to celebrate National Business Week, another version
